15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 25 O.S. 2021, Section 82.2, is
16 amended to read as follows:
17 Section 82.2. The following additional days are designated as
18 holidays:
19 Jefferson Day on the 13th day of April; Oklahoma Day on the 22nd
20 day of April; Mother’s Day on the second Sunday in May; Juneteenth
21 National Freedom Day on the third Saturday in June; Indian Day on
22 the first Saturday after the full moon in September; Cherokee Strip
23 Day on the 16th day of September; Will Rogers Day on the 4th day of
24 November; President Donald J. Trump Day on the 5th day of November;
